  "body": "Both in the remix.ethereum and test networks any getter function is free of gas and does not return a transaction hash. Do the main ethereum network offer the same behaviour? What is the reasoning behind making a getter function free if it requires a small amount of work?\r\n\r\nThank you so much!",
