    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Getter functions don't require any work from miners, so they are free. They simply read from whatever Ethereum node you're connected to, rather than having to be transmitted throughout the network and included in a block.\r\n\r\nSee also, the difference between eth.sendTransaction and eth.call:\r\n* https://github.com/ethereum/wiki/wiki/JavaScript-API#web3ethsendtransaction (costs gas)\r\n* https://github.com/ethereum/wiki/wiki/JavaScript-API#web3ethcall (is free)",
